            rdf:_1          [:hasSpeaker :aanya  ;
                            :hasText    """Hello Jack, I am [Aanya Patel](https://www.example.org/aanya) [from](http://xmlns.com/foaf/spec/#Organization) [CorpCorp](https://www.example.org/SpecialParts). Thank you for forwarding your offer to us. 
